\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/caller\"><code>Function.prototype.caller</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/displayName\"><code>Function.prototype.displayName</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/length\"><code>Function.prototype.length</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/name\"><code>Function.prototype.name</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/prototype\"><code>Function.prototype.prototype</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methoden</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/apply\"><code>Function.prototype.apply()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/bind\"><code>Function.prototype.bind()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/call\"><code>Function.prototype.call()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/toString\"><code>Function.prototype.toString()</code></a></li></ol></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Eigenschaften</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor\"><code>Object.prototype.constructor</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methoden</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"> <div class=\"notecard warning\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Kein Standard:</strong> Diese Funktion entspricht nicht dem Standard und ist nicht Teil der Standardisierung. Diese Funktion darf nicht in Webseiten, die via das Internet zugänglich sind, benutzt werden: Sie wird nicht für alle Nutzer funktionieren. Es kann zu umfangreichen Inkompatibilitäten zwischen verschiedenen Implementierungen kommen und die Funktionsweise oder Eigenschaften könnten in der Zukunft verändert werden.</p></div></div>\n\n<p>Das <strong><code>InternalError</code> Objekt</strong> zeigt einen Fehler an, der in der JavaScript-Umgebung auftritt. Zum Beispiel: <strong>\"InternalError</strong>: too much recursion\".</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">new InternalError([<var>message</var>[, <var>fileName</var>[, <var>lineNumber</var>]]])</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameter","title":"Parameter","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"message\"><code>message</code></dt>\n <dd>Optional. Für Menschen lesbare Fehlerbeschreibung.</dd>\n <dt id=\"filename\"><code>fileName</code> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Optional. Der Name der Datei, in der der Fehler auftritt.</dd>\n <dt id=\"linenumber\"><code>lineNumber</code> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Optional. Die Zeilennummer in der Datei, in der der Fehler auftritt.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beschreibung","title":"Beschreibung","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Ein <code>InternalError</code> wird immer erzeugt, wenn ein Fehler in der JavaScript-Umgebung auftritt.</p>\n\n<p>Beispielfälle die oft eintreten, wenn manchmal etwas zu ang ist:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>\"too many switch cases\",</li>\n <li>\"too many parentheses in regular expression\",</li>\n <li>\"array initializer too large\",</li>\n <li>\"too much recursion\".</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"eigenschaften","title":"Eigenschaften","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"internalerror.prototype_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/InternalError\"><code>InternalError.prototype</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Erlaubt das Hinzufügen von Eigenschaften zu einem <code>InternalError</code> Objekt.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methoden","title":"Methoden","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Die globale <code>InternalError</code> Klasse enthält keine eigenen Methoden, jedoch erbt sie einige Methoden durch die Prototypenkette.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"internalerror_instanzen","title":"<code>InternalError</code> Instanzen","isH3":false,"content":"","titleAsText":"InternalError Instanzen"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"eigenschaften_2","title":"Eigenschaften","isH3":true,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\">{{page('/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/InternalError/prototype', 'Eigenschaften')}}</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"Methods","isH3":true,"content":"<div id=\"sect4\">{{page('/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/InternalError/prototype', 'Methoden')}}</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<p>In keiner Spezifikation enthalten.</p>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.InternalError","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/InternalError/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect5\">\n<div id=\"sect6\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Error\"><code>Error</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/InternalError\"><code>InternalError.prototype</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beschreibung","id":"beschreibung"},{"text":"Eigenschaften","id":"eigenschaften"},{"text":"Methoden","id":"methoden"},{"text":"<code>InternalError</code> Instanzen","id":"internalerror_instanzen"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Das InternalError Objekt zeigt einen Fehler an, der in der JavaScript-Umgebung a